Questions:
If you choose not to participate in the IMPACT Study, what will be the impact on your standard medical care?

A) Your standard medical care will be discontinued; 
B) Your standard medical care will remain unaffected; 
C) You will be required to pay additional costs for your standard medical care; 
D) You will not be able to access genetic testing services in the future.

Correct answer: B

If you experience an injury as a result of participating in the IMPACT study, whom should you contact for assistance?

A) The VUMC Institutional Review Board Office;
B) Tuya Pal, MD, FACMG, the Principal Investigator;
C) Your personal healthcare provider;
D) The National Institutes of Health (NIH).

Correct answer: B) Tuya Pal, MD, FACMG, the Principal Investigator.
